title: Hour 1 - NBA Finals 3-Pt Contest, Fitzmagic Retires, Chirs Mannix
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NBA Finals 3-Pt Contest, Fitzmagic Retires, Chirs Mannix
description:
Dan is surprised the Celtics came out on top of the NBA Finals Game 1, 3-pt contest. He talks about NFL veteran QB Ryan Fitzpatrick retiring. And Chris Mannix drops by for some NBA Finals analysis.
